               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Sǝnkǝssar “Synaxarion” for the second half of the year (fols.
                     3ra-150vc) 
 I-1) Maggābit (fols. 3ra-28rc)
 I-2) Miyāzyā (fols.
                     28va-47rc) 
 I-3) Gǝnbot (fols. 47ra-71vc) 
 I-4) Sane (fols.
                     71va-94rc) 
 I-5) Ḥamle (fols. 94va-121vc) 
 I-6) Naḥāse (fols.
                     121va-145vc) 
 I-7) Ṗagʷǝmen (fols. 145vc-150vc) 
 - Za-ʾaqrabku
                     māḥleta… “The song I am offering…” (concluding prayer): fol. 150vc
 The
                     commemorative notices are followed by ʿarke-hymns
 
 Additio
                     1.</summary>
