                        <seg type="rubrication">Nomina sacra; the word salām; several groups of
                           lines alternating with balck lines on the incipit page of every month;
                           incipit of each commemorative notice; elements of the punctuation signs;
                           elements of Ethiopic numerals.</seg>
                     </handNote>
